openmediavault-snapraid-aio (8.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add per-config scheduling: Schedule button on datatable, each config
    gets its own cron entry; removes global enable toggle and Settings page
  * Add Tools submenu: Sync, Force Sync, Run Now, and Last Log actions;
    Sync and Force Sync run snapraid directly; Run Now and Last Log use
    the AIO script; all stream output live via taskDialog
  * Add Last Run column to config list datatable: timestamp and outcome
    (OK / WARNING / Started) parsed from /var/log/snapraid.log
  * Add email_notifications toggle per config: sender and receiver pulled
    read-only from OMV system notification settings
  * Add Test Apprise and Test Apprise email buttons to config form: test
    each notification channel directly from the saved config
  * Add openmediavault-snapraid to Depends: plugin is non-functional
    without the OMV SnapRAID plugin
  * Improve SnapRAID array selector: show array name instead of raw path;
    resolve symlinks to stable UUID-based paths; hide legacy symlink
  * Switch Apprise URL field to tagInput: supports multiple URLs as chips
  * Disable Telegram and Discord integrations (superseded by Apprise)
  * Delete /etc/snapraid-aio-*.conf files on package purge
  * Add confdb migration script for 8.1: removes stale enable, docker_local,
    docker_remote, docker_user, docker_host_services nodes from existing DB
    entries to prevent Salt rendering failures on upgrade
  * Move ignore_pattern field to end of Sync Thresholds section
  * Fix Docker container list sort order: sort alphabetically by name

 -- OpenMediaVault Plugin Developers <plugins@omv-extras.org>  Wed, 16 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000

